yingyinNormal.zh: 你父亲的葬礼你都没来，却为这件事来？

yingyinNormal.en: Now you're wigging out at a rat funeral. You're making me nervous.
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在你又在耗子的葬礼上抽风，你让我很紧张。

yingyinNormal.en: Check it out. Giants-Cowboys. You're watching a football game at a funeral?
yingyinNormal.zh: 瞧，巨人队对牛仔队。你在葬礼时看足球赛？

yingyinNormal.en: What sort of service will it be? Not a funeral. I've decided not to disturb him.
yingyinNormal.zh: 打算举办什么仪式？不是葬礼，我不想惊扰他。

yingyinNormal.en: However, just in case it doesn't work out, I decided to plan this pre-funeral.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但是，万一不行的话，就先安排一场生前的葬礼。

yingyinNormal.en: Dear America, remember that astronaut we killed and had a really nice funeral for?
yingyinNormal.zh: 亲爱的美国，还记得那个被我们弄死的了还办了特别好的葬礼的宇航员吗？

yingyinNormal.en: If you speak to her, tell her the funeral's tomorrow. I'm sorry, monsieur, they have gone away.
yingyinNormal.zh: 要是碰到她，告诉她葬礼在明天。很抱歉，先生，他们已经走了。

yingyinNormal.en: Monica and I have a grandmother who died, you both went to her funeral, name that grandmother.
yingyinNormal.zh: 莫妮卡和我的外婆过世时，两位都参加了她的葬礼，我们祖母叫什么名字？

yingyinNormal.en: Penny, did you and Leonard ever discuss funeral arrangements? I think she meant something a little happier.
yingyinNormal.zh: 佩妮，你和莱纳德讨论过葬礼的安排吗？她是说聊点开心的事情。

yingyinNormal.en: What we are proposing is that the funeral takes place this Thursday, the 9th, 4:00 pm, at St. Paul's.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们的提议是葬礼于本周四(9号)下午四点举行，放在圣保罗大教堂。

yingyinNormal.en: I wanted to attend my own funeral. I mean, I'm hopeful that I'll be able to attend as a ghost, but…
yingyinNormal.zh: 我想参加我自己的葬礼。我是说，我希望到时候是我的鬼魂去参加，但是……

yingyinNormal.en: Sheldon, when the president of the university is giving a eulogy at a funeral, don't yawn and point at your watch.
yingyinNormal.zh: 谢尔顿，我们大学校长在葬礼上念悼词时，别打哈欠外加指手表催他。

yingyinNormal.en: Well done. No, hold on. No. You brought me to a stranger's funeral? Memorial service. Whatever.
yingyinNormal.zh: 任务完成了。不不不，等等，你把我带到一个陌生人的葬礼上来？追悼会。管它叫什么。

yingyinNormal.en: I rang, I wrote, I implored. But not a single one of the sparkling hundreds that enjoyed his hospitality attended the funeral.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我打电话，写信，苦苦哀求，但受过他款待的人没一个来参加他的葬礼。

yingyinNormal.en: Sending Samantha off to college. Sending you off to college. You know what's next? Huh? It's my fucking funeral.
yingyinNormal.zh: 送萨曼塔上大学，送你上大学。你知道下一个里程碑是什么吗？嗯？是我他妈的葬礼。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, right. Yeah, sisters. Like, we're obligated to see each other on Thanksgiving, Christmas, Luke's funeral. I'm fine!
yingyinNormal.zh: 对啊，我们是姐妹。每个节假日我们都要看见对方，感恩节，圣诞节，卢克的葬礼。我没事！

yingyinNormal.en: If anything happens to me, 007, I need you to do something. Find a man called Marco Sciarra. Kill him. And don't miss the funeral.
yingyinNormal.zh: 要是我出了事，007，我需要你帮我做件事，找到一个叫马科·斯基亚拉的人，杀了他，还有不要错过葬礼。

yingyinNormal.en: Amy. Amy. Oh, right, funeral. Amy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 艾米，艾米，忘了是要去丧礼，艾米。

yingyinNormal.en: Garboni Funeral Home? Thanks for coming.
yingyinNormal.zh: 加伯尼殡仪馆？感谢出席。
